"powershell.exe" "-Command $version='1.0.0.0'$application='CitrixVPN'$path=[Environment]::GetFolderPath('CommonApplicationData')$logfile=\"$path\citrix\agee\intune.log\"$jsfile=\"$path\citrix\agee\intune.js\"class conn{[string]$name; [string]$url; [string]$cert}class config{  [long]$btime   [bool]$auto_open_homepage  [conn[]]$connections  [bool]$debug_logging  [string]$language  [string]$userAgent  [bool]$local_lan_access  [bool]$disableL3  [long]$etime }function Write-Log([string]$label,[string]$msg){  $out=if($msg -ne ''){$label+': '+$msg}else{$label}  Add-Content -Path $logfile $out -Passthru}function Rotate-Logs{  if (Test-Path $logfile){    Copy-Item -Path $logfile -Destination \"$logfile.backup\" -Force    Remove-Item -Path $logfile -Force  }  Write-Log '========================='  Write-Log $application  Write-Log 'Date' (Get-Date -Format yyyy-MM-dd)  Write-Log 'Time' (Get-Date -Format hh:mm:ss)  Write-Log 'Version' $version  Write-Log '========================='}function Get-CompressedJson([config]$c){  $j=ConvertTo-Json -Compress $c  $j=$j -replace 'auto_open_homepage','auto open homepage'  $j=$j -replace 'local_lan_access','local lan access'  $j=$j -replace 'debug_logging','debug logging'  return $j}function Compare-ByteArrays([string]$a1,[string]$a2,[int]$start,[int]$end) {  for($i=$start;$i -lt $end;$i++){    if($a1[$i] -ne $a2[$i]){      return $false     }  }  return $true }function Compare-Configs([string]$j,[int]$compareoffset){  $jsworkspace=\"$jsfile.backup\"  Set-Content -Path $jsworkspace -Value $j -Encoding Ascii  if((Test-Path $jsfile) -eq $true){    $f=Get-Content $jsfile     if($f.Length -ne $j.Length){      Write-Log 'Configurations have different length:'      Write-Log $f    }    elseif((Compare-ByteArrays $f $j $compareoffset ($j.Length-$compareoffset)) -eq $false){      Write-Log 'Configurations are different:'      Write-Log $f    }    else{      Write-Log 'No change to configuration:'      Write-Log $f      return    }  }  Copy-Item -Path $jsworkspace -Destination $jsfile -Force  Write-Log 'Update configuration:'  Write-Log $j}function Get-TextElement([Xml.XmlNode]$x, [string]$tag){  $node=$x.GetElementsByTagName($tag)  if($node.Count -eq 0){return $null}  return $node[0].'#text'}function Get-BoolElement([Xml.XmlNode]$x, [string]$tag){  $node=$x.GetElementsByTagName($tag)  if($node.Count -eq 0){return $false}  if($node[0].'#text' -eq 'true'){return $true}  return $false}function Parse-Config([Xml.XmlNode]$x){  $c=New-Object config  $friend=$x.GetElementsByTagName('FriendlyName')  $server=$x.GetElementsByTagName('ServerName')  $cert=$x.GetElementsByTagName('Cert')  $max=if($server.Count -lt $friendCount){$server.Count}else{$friend.Count}  for($i=0;$i -lt $max;$i++){    $nuc=New-Object conn    $nuc.name=$friend[$i].'#text'    $nuc.url=$server[$i].'#text'    $nuc.cert=$cert[$i].'#text'    $c.connections+=$nuc  }  $c.language=Get-TextElement $x 'language'  $c.userAgent=Get-TextElement $x 'useragent'  $c.auto_open_homepage=Get-BoolElement $x 'auto_open_homepage'  $c.debug_logging=Get-BoolElement $x 'debug_logging'  $c.local_lan_access=Get-BoolElement $x 'local_lan_access'  $c.disableL3=Get-BoolElement $x 'disableL3'  $c.btime=$c.etime=(Get-Date).ticks  return $c}if([Environment]::OsVersion.Version.Major -ge 10){  Rotate-Logs  ForEach($vc in Get-VpnConnection -AllUserConnection){    Write-Log 'Checking VPN connection' $vc.Name    if(($vc.VpnConfigurationXml.GetElementsByTagName($application).ToString() -ne '') -or ($vc.PlugInApplicationID.StartsWith($application))){      Write-Log 'Found' $application      $conf=Parse-Config $vc.VpnConfigurationXml      $json=CompressedJson $conf      Write-Log 'Ticks' $conf.btime      Compare-Configs $json (([string]$conf.btime).Length+'{\"btime\":'.Length)      Write-Log '========================='      return     }  }  if(Test-Path $jsfile){	Remove-Item -Force $jsfile -Confirm:$false 	}  Write-Log 'No VPN connection matching' $application  Write-Log '========================='}"
